fr.apteryx.imageio.dicom
Class Tag

Object
  Tag

public abstract class Tag
extends Object

An abstract class defining constants for the DICOM 2007 standard data elements and some convenient static methods to manipulate tags. Attributes that have been retired from the DICOM standard have their tag marked as deprecated.
